      "text": "One might take inspiration from our framework try to use MAML for zero-shot task performance by transforming task representations would require adopting our meta-mapping framework, as well as a number of ideas of our architecture (where do the task representations come from, and how are they used?), and so its not clear to us that this is an appropriate baseline, rather than simply another implementation of our technique.",
