      "review_id": "B1ez1LvJcB",
      "rebuttal_id": "rygJHT4DoB",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "text": "We remained with synthetic tasks for two reasons: 1) to illustrate the method in settings we thought would be clearer, 2) because as we highlight in the future directions, there is a lack of meta-learning datasets that contain as structured of relationships between tasks as we consider.",
